WEBVTT

00:10:30.644 --> 00:10:33.414
Ni rahisi katika uchumi huu wa kisiasa
na dunia

00:10:33.438 --> 00:10:36.488
kutaka kukata tamaatunapofikiria kubadilisha serikali.

00:10:37.386 --> 00:10:40.887
Ni rahisi kujiuzulu kutoka kwa wajibu tu kwa kufikiria

00:10:40.911 --> 00:10:43.253
kuwa serikali haina ufanisi,

00:10:43.277 --> 00:10:44.433
ina rushwa mno,

00:10:44.457 --> 00:10:45.688
hairekebishiki.

00:10:46.527 --> 00:10:49.964
Huenda tukapata majukumu muhimu katika serikali

00:10:49.988 --> 00:10:51.188
katika sekta nyingine,

00:10:51.212 --> 00:10:52.381
katika suluhisho la utoaji misaada,

00:10:52.405 --> 00:10:54.973
au kukata tu tamaa na kujisikia wanyonge.

00:10:56.029 --> 00:10:59.912
Lakini, kwa sababu tu mfumo unaumwa haina maana unakufa.